WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.710
Well, I'm doing this prayer video

00:00:02.720 --> 00:00:04.470
live because I was going to make a

00:00:04.480 --> 00:00:08.390
video already today for

00:00:08.400 --> 00:00:11.270
tomorrow. But after I got all

00:00:11.280 --> 00:00:13.190
the emails for the earthquake that just

00:00:13.200 --> 00:00:16.150
took place off the coast of Russia,

00:00:16.160 --> 00:00:19.349
I felt led to pray over people's

00:00:19.359 --> 00:00:21.029
protection because of the tsunami

00:00:21.039 --> 00:00:23.750
warnings that they're having. And so, I

00:00:23.760 --> 00:00:25.189
want everybody to come together, and

00:00:25.199 --> 00:00:26.790
we're just going to take authority and

00:00:26.800 --> 00:00:30.230
pray over the coastlines of

00:00:30.240 --> 00:00:34.389
Hawaii, Japan, the West Coast of

00:00:34.399 --> 00:00:36.389
the United States of America, and parts

00:00:36.399 --> 00:00:38.790
of Alaska because, you know, we have power

00:00:38.800 --> 00:00:40.310
and authority over all this stuff,

00:00:40.320 --> 00:00:42.709
folks. And so, we'll put our

00:00:42.719 --> 00:00:44.790
angels out there watching over these

00:00:44.800 --> 00:00:47.910
people. We're the salt and we're the

00:00:47.920 --> 00:00:49.830
light, and that's what our job is.

00:00:49.840 --> 00:00:52.389
And when God gives us these

00:00:52.399 --> 00:00:54.790
harbingers, these warnings

00:00:54.800 --> 00:00:56.310
through prayer telling us that they

00:00:56.320 --> 00:00:57.670
were coming... How many weeks ago? He

00:00:57.680 --> 00:00:59.029
said, "A major one is about to take

00:00:59.029 --> 00:00:59.039
place."And

00:00:59.039 --> 00:01:01.189
it did, just like the Lord

00:01:01.199 --> 00:01:04.630
told us. But it's not the

00:01:04.630 --> 00:01:04.640
one—I've

00:01:04.640 --> 00:01:06.310
seen that one up there, and then I

00:01:06.320 --> 00:01:09.350
see the one on the Oregon coastline, and

00:01:09.360 --> 00:01:11.429
it will be very devastating from what I

00:01:11.439 --> 00:01:14.469
have seen. So, we take authority and

00:01:14.479 --> 00:01:16.630
pray over the people of Oregon and over

00:01:16.640 --> 00:01:18.390
Washington because it's the Ring of

00:01:18.400 --> 00:01:20.630
Fire. And this is the pressure that I

00:01:20.640 --> 00:01:23.270
warned you all about that's coming,

00:01:23.280 --> 00:01:25.749
a shaking in the atmosphere,

00:01:25.749 --> 00:01:25.759
a

00:01:25.759 --> 00:01:28.070
shaking in the soil. And the Lord told

00:01:28.080 --> 00:01:29.910
me, He said, "Great pressure will come

00:01:29.920 --> 00:01:32.950
on the soil in the days

00:01:32.950 --> 00:01:32.960
ahead."And

00:01:32.960 --> 00:01:33.910
then there's other

00:01:33.920 --> 00:01:35.429
articles that are being sent to us about

00:01:35.439 --> 00:01:36.950
the asteroids saying, "Hey, it's going

00:01:36.960 --> 00:01:38.630
to hit the moon."Now, I thought

00:01:38.640 --> 00:01:40.789
that was kind of interesting because of

00:01:40.799 --> 00:01:42.870
what the Lord was telling me about the

00:01:42.880 --> 00:01:45.670
tides. He said, "The tides will change.

00:01:45.680 --> 00:01:49.350
There'll be unusual tides. They'll come

00:01:49.360 --> 00:01:51.990
further in than ever before."And He

00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:53.429
said, "And they'll go out further than

00:01:53.439 --> 00:01:55.670
they ever have before."He said, "Watch

00:01:55.680 --> 00:01:57.749
the tides,"if you all remember. And so,

00:01:57.759 --> 00:01:59.270
these are the things that I've been

00:01:59.280 --> 00:02:01.270
praying over.

00:02:01.280 --> 00:02:05.109
And over Italy—unusual tides in

00:02:05.119 --> 00:02:08.150
Italy, over... was it Venice? Yeah,

00:02:08.160 --> 00:02:09.190
that's what the Lord was talking to me

00:02:09.200 --> 00:02:11.990
about. And so, those are the

00:02:12.000 --> 00:02:13.430
things that I've been praying over. But

00:02:13.440 --> 00:02:15.589
I can tell you what's happened in

00:02:15.599 --> 00:02:17.670
the last couple of days with me.

00:02:17.680 --> 00:02:19.110
But maybe we'll just go straight into

00:02:19.120 --> 00:02:21.589
prayer today on this video. I was

00:02:21.599 --> 00:02:23.270
going to talk about some things the Lord

00:02:23.280 --> 00:02:25.990
had for you; I guess I can go over that.

00:02:28.319 --> 00:02:31.030
He was talking about being obedient and listening

00:02:31.030 --> 00:02:31.040
to

00:02:31.040 --> 00:02:33.990
his still small voice, and

00:02:34.000 --> 00:02:35.910
that it wouldn't have to be, you

00:02:35.920 --> 00:02:38.790
know, like with body language

00:02:38.800 --> 00:02:41.430
and how you can sense

00:02:41.440 --> 00:02:43.830
whenever your spouse is upset about

00:02:43.840 --> 00:02:45.750
something. They don't have to use words.

00:02:45.760 --> 00:02:48.470
But following the voice of God so strong,

00:02:48.470 --> 00:02:48.480
following

00:02:48.480 --> 00:02:50.710
that inward peace,

00:02:50.710 --> 00:02:50.720
so

00:02:50.720 --> 00:02:52.630
that He doesn't have to

00:02:52.630 --> 00:02:52.640
speak

00:02:52.640 --> 00:02:54.470
when you're mature

00:02:54.480 --> 00:02:56.070
and you've been around somebody a long

00:02:56.080 --> 00:02:58.070
time. They don't have to say something.

00:02:58.080 --> 00:02:59.750
A lot of times, you already know what

00:02:59.760 --> 00:03:01.350
they're feeling just by how they're

00:03:01.360 --> 00:03:03.589
acting, right? And your wife,

00:03:03.599 --> 00:03:05.270
you know, you're sitting next to

00:03:05.280 --> 00:03:06.710
your wife in the car or something, and

00:03:06.720 --> 00:03:08.309
you know if there's something

00:03:08.319 --> 00:03:10.630
bothering her or not just because of

00:03:10.630 --> 00:03:10.640
her

00:03:10.640 --> 00:03:13.670
mannerisms, right? And so, that was

00:03:13.680 --> 00:03:15.670
what the Lord was talking to

00:03:15.680 --> 00:03:17.030
me about—listening to the

00:03:17.040 --> 00:03:19.589
mannerisms, listening to Him.

00:03:19.589 --> 00:03:19.599
He doesn't

00:03:19.599 --> 00:03:21.670
have to... If He's not saying something,

00:03:21.680 --> 00:03:23.509
follow that peace that passes

00:03:23.519 --> 00:03:25.830
all understanding. There's many of you...

00:03:25.840 --> 00:03:28.149
There's so much confusion,

00:03:28.159 --> 00:03:29.910
and that's why I see the

00:03:29.920 --> 00:03:32.149
emails. My wife tells me, she says, "Brandon,

00:03:32.159 --> 00:03:33.509
people are thinking they're hearing the

00:03:33.519 --> 00:03:35.830
Lord, Brandon, and they're not. They're

00:03:35.840 --> 00:03:37.750
not. There are familiar spirits that

00:03:37.760 --> 00:03:40.630
are messing with these

00:03:40.630 --> 00:03:40.640
people."And

00:03:40.640 --> 00:03:43.589
that's why I made the video today

00:03:43.599 --> 00:03:47.030
going back to the ABCs of Christianity:

00:03:47.040 --> 00:03:49.350
reading your Bible, praying, going

00:03:49.360 --> 00:03:51.030
to church, volunteering, doing the

00:03:51.040 --> 00:03:52.949
things that you've got to do. Do the ABCs,

00:03:52.959 --> 00:03:55.430
but don't just go around hearing

00:03:55.440 --> 00:03:56.949
voices. That's what I was talking about.

00:03:56.959 --> 00:03:58.070
There's a lot of people just hearing

00:03:58.080 --> 00:03:59.589
voices. They're, you know, "I

00:03:59.599 --> 00:04:01.589
hear this voice and I followed it and I

00:04:01.599 --> 00:04:03.910
did this,"and I'm thinking, "Well, don't

00:04:03.920 --> 00:04:06.070
do that."You've got to test the spirits and you've got to

00:04:06.080 --> 00:04:07.750
pray in the spirit,

00:04:07.760 --> 00:04:09.270
or pray in English, whatever you know

00:04:09.280 --> 00:04:12.789
how to do. Pray, worship, get into

00:04:12.799 --> 00:04:14.789
worship. And I have this for

00:04:14.799 --> 00:04:17.030
you: I was hurting really bad in my hip. I

00:04:17.040 --> 00:04:19.110
hadn't made a video because I don't

00:04:19.120 --> 00:04:21.749
know what I did, but it was so bad I

00:04:21.759 --> 00:04:24.310
couldn't even get out of my chair. I was

00:04:24.320 --> 00:04:26.710
under attack, and it was hurting

00:04:26.720 --> 00:04:29.830
so bad I couldn't move. And so, I laid

00:04:29.840 --> 00:04:31.270
down and I couldn't even turn over

00:04:31.270 --> 00:04:31.280
in

00:04:31.280 --> 00:04:33.030
bed. It was the most

00:04:33.040 --> 00:04:37.430
excruciating pain I've ever had.

00:04:37.440 --> 00:04:39.189
And I told my wife, I said, "I might

00:04:39.199 --> 00:04:40.870
have to have you take me to the

00:04:40.880 --> 00:04:42.390
hospital because that's how bad this

00:04:42.400 --> 00:04:43.749
is."And

00:04:43.759 --> 00:04:46.310
all of a sudden, I started praying.

00:04:46.320 --> 00:04:47.510
And I was praying and praying and

00:04:47.520 --> 00:04:48.870
praying and praying. I said, "Lord, I

00:04:48.880 --> 00:04:49.990
thank you that I'm healed,"and all this

00:04:50.000 --> 00:04:51.749
stuff. He said, "Stop praying and start

00:04:51.759 --> 00:04:55.590
worshiping.

00:04:55.600 --> 00:04:58.710
Start worshiping me."So, I just

00:04:58.720 --> 00:05:01.110
started singing songs,

00:05:01.120 --> 00:05:03.030
started worshiping the Father in here,

00:05:03.040 --> 00:05:04.390
and the glory of the Lord started to

00:05:04.400 --> 00:05:06.469
come. I could feel it. And in His

00:05:06.479 --> 00:05:07.909
presence, there's fullness of joy;

00:05:07.919 --> 00:05:09.189
there's fullness of peace. And I was

00:05:09.199 --> 00:05:11.110
still feeling that pain, and He said,

00:05:11.120 --> 00:05:13.430
"Move your leg."I said, "Move my leg? I'm in pain! I don't

00:05:13.430 --> 00:05:13.440
want to move my leg."He

00:05:13.440 --> 00:05:17.029
said, "Move your leg."Okay, so

00:05:17.029 --> 00:05:17.039
I moved

00:05:17.039 --> 00:05:19.270
my leg, and

00:05:19.270 --> 00:05:19.280
I lifted

00:05:19.280 --> 00:05:23.590
my leg.

00:05:26.479 --> 00:05:28.629
And all of a sudden, out of that little

00:05:28.639 --> 00:05:31.590
bit of obedience, the pain subsided a

00:05:31.600 --> 00:05:33.510
little bit.

00:05:33.520 --> 00:05:36.310
He said, "Sing."So, I started

00:05:36.320 --> 00:05:39.749
singing, and I moved my leg. He

00:05:39.759 --> 00:05:41.909
said, "Stop moving your leg. Tell Diana

00:05:41.919 --> 00:05:44.710
to sing."So, she started singing,

00:05:44.720 --> 00:05:47.350
started worshiping, and all of a sudden,

00:05:47.360 --> 00:05:49.110
that pain level went down a little bit

00:05:49.120 --> 00:05:51.350
more. I said, "Well, my goodness, this

00:05:51.360 --> 00:05:53.670
is amazing."Because I'm

00:05:53.680 --> 00:05:55.270
telling you, it was on a scale

00:05:55.270 --> 00:05:55.280
of

00:05:55.280 --> 00:05:57.189
one to 10, it was a 20. That's how bad

00:05:57.199 --> 00:05:59.510
this pain was. It was

00:05:59.520 --> 00:06:03.350
awful, and I was crying out. I

00:06:03.360 --> 00:06:05.670
said, "I need mercy right

00:06:05.670 --> 00:06:05.680
now."He

00:06:05.680 --> 00:06:07.670
said,

00:06:07.670 --> 00:06:07.680
"Sing."So,

00:06:07.680 --> 00:06:09.029
I started singing more. He said,

00:06:09.039 --> 00:06:12.150
"Lift your leg."So, I lifted my leg and

00:06:12.160 --> 00:06:15.590
I moved my leg. He said... It's just

00:06:15.600 --> 00:06:17.430
the still small voice. It's the

00:06:17.440 --> 00:06:19.270
obedience of the little thing, even if

00:06:19.280 --> 00:06:22.070
it sounds foolish. Listen. He

00:06:22.080 --> 00:06:25.029
said, "Turn your body over, get on

00:06:25.039 --> 00:06:26.790
the floor, and move yourself where

00:06:26.800 --> 00:06:28.390
you can stand on one foot and

00:06:28.390 --> 00:06:28.400
hop."I

00:06:28.400 --> 00:06:37.029
said, "Lord, I'm in

00:06:37.029 --> 00:06:37.039
excruciating pain."But

00:06:37.039 --> 00:06:39.110
I said, "Lord, I'll do it."So, I

00:06:39.120 --> 00:06:41.029
turned over out of the side of my bed

00:06:41.039 --> 00:06:44.070
and I started bouncing on the foot that

00:06:44.080 --> 00:06:46.550
didn't hurt, and the pain started lifting

00:06:46.560 --> 00:06:49.830
even more.

00:06:49.840 --> 00:06:51.350
I said, "Well, that was really

00:06:51.350 --> 00:06:51.360
interesting."And

00:06:51.360 --> 00:06:53.270
now, I was able to move

00:06:53.280 --> 00:06:54.790
a little bit so I could go to the

00:06:54.800 --> 00:06:56.870
restroom. So, He said, "Go to the

00:06:56.880 --> 00:06:58.469
restroom."So,

00:06:58.479 --> 00:07:00.309
I hobbled into the restroom, and by

00:07:00.319 --> 00:07:01.909
the time I got

00:07:01.909 --> 00:07:01.919
there,

00:07:01.919 --> 00:07:04.469
the pain lifted a little bit more. And

00:07:04.479 --> 00:07:06.790
then He said, "Now, sing more."So, I

00:07:06.800 --> 00:07:08.710
started singing more and I started

00:07:08.720 --> 00:07:11.270
worshiping the Father. "Thank you, Father.

00:07:11.280 --> 00:07:14.390
Thank you."I made it to the hall, and

00:07:14.400 --> 00:07:16.629
He said, "Walk quickly."I said, "Walk? I can barely."So,

00:07:16.629 --> 00:07:16.639
I hobbled,

00:07:16.639 --> 00:07:18.469
starting

00:07:18.479 --> 00:07:20.230
to move down the hall, and the pain

00:07:20.240 --> 00:07:22.629
lifted a little bit more.

00:07:22.639 --> 00:07:24.309
And I told her, "It's

00:07:24.309 --> 00:07:24.319
lifting."But

00:07:24.319 --> 00:07:27.029
it's as I take every single

00:07:27.039 --> 00:07:29.990
step of obedience in what He's asking me

00:07:30.000 --> 00:07:31.990
to do, even if it's not something that

00:07:32.000 --> 00:07:34.629
my flesh wants to do. I'm following the

00:07:34.639 --> 00:07:37.110
voice of God and what He's instructed me,

00:07:37.120 --> 00:07:40.870
even if it doesn't make sense.

00:07:40.880 --> 00:07:42.790
So, I get down all the

00:07:42.800 --> 00:07:44.150
way, and He said, "Now, go sit on the side

00:07:44.160 --> 00:07:45.909
of your bed again."So, all

00:07:45.919 --> 00:07:48.390
these little steps

00:07:48.400 --> 00:07:52.070
of pain that was so intense

00:07:52.080 --> 00:07:54.469
that I couldn't move... and I kept

00:07:54.479 --> 00:07:55.990
listening, I kept listening, I kept

00:07:56.000 --> 00:07:59.350
listening. And by the time it was like

00:07:59.350 --> 00:07:59.360
1:00,

00:07:59.360 --> 00:08:00.790
whatever it was, it was

00:08:00.800 --> 00:08:02.950
terrible. Boom, it just started lifting

00:08:02.960 --> 00:08:04.950
completely. And He said, "Go to

00:08:04.950 --> 00:08:04.960
sleep."So,

00:08:04.960 --> 00:08:06.550
I went to sleep. When I woke up, it

00:08:06.560 --> 00:08:08.469
was completely gone.

00:08:08.479 --> 00:08:10.309
But what I'm trying to tell you is in

00:08:10.319 --> 00:08:12.710
the word that He gave me within that

00:08:12.720 --> 00:08:15.670
24 hours, He said, "This is what it's

00:08:15.680 --> 00:08:17.749
going to take

00:08:17.759 --> 00:08:20.790
to walk in the greater

00:08:20.790 --> 00:08:20.800
glory."Even

00:08:20.800 --> 00:08:22.950
if it doesn't make sense what

00:08:22.960 --> 00:08:27.189
I'm instructing you to do, you

00:08:27.199 --> 00:08:30.390
just obey me even if it's painful. Do

00:08:30.400 --> 00:08:32.630
you understand? Following the voice of

00:08:32.640 --> 00:08:36.389
God beyond your intellect

00:08:36.399 --> 00:08:39.110
in these last days, even if it doesn't

00:08:39.120 --> 00:08:41.589
make sense to your natural mind. The

00:08:41.599 --> 00:08:43.589
natural man perceiveth not the things of

00:08:43.599 --> 00:08:46.790
the Lord. And in these last days, for

00:08:46.800 --> 00:08:49.190
what's about to take place, you must

00:08:49.200 --> 00:08:51.509
obey Him at all costs, even if it

00:08:51.519 --> 00:08:53.750
doesn't make sense. "Jump on one leg.""I'm

00:08:53.750 --> 00:08:53.760
in pain.""Jump

00:08:53.760 --> 00:08:56.389
on one leg."Boing, boing,

00:08:56.399 --> 00:09:01.110
boing. It lifts. I go, "Well, I'll

00:09:01.110 --> 00:09:01.120
be."And

00:09:01.120 --> 00:09:03.110
that's what He was talking to

00:09:03.120 --> 00:09:06.790
me about—obeying Him at all costs. And He

00:09:06.800 --> 00:09:08.310
gave me an illustration because I

00:09:08.320 --> 00:09:11.430
watched Billy Burke.

00:09:11.440 --> 00:09:14.230
He'll be ministering to somebody, and all

00:09:14.240 --> 00:09:17.110
of a sudden, he will get a word of

00:09:17.120 --> 00:09:21.910
knowledge for another person

00:09:21.920 --> 00:09:24.230
instantaneously. He'll turn and

00:09:24.240 --> 00:09:26.389
minister that word of knowledge that

00:09:26.399 --> 00:09:27.590
he's getting from the Father

00:09:27.600 --> 00:09:29.269
instantaneously to that other person.

00:09:29.279 --> 00:09:30.470
The other person's there, and it's

00:09:30.480 --> 00:09:32.230
awkward,

00:09:32.240 --> 00:09:33.750
and they'll be looking at him like

00:09:33.760 --> 00:09:35.750
you're rude. But

00:09:35.760 --> 00:09:38.150
he'll follow the

00:09:38.160 --> 00:09:41.430
voice of God at all

00:09:41.430 --> 00:09:41.440
costs,

00:09:41.440 --> 00:09:44.230
and the anointing follows. It flows.

00:09:44.240 --> 00:09:46.230
It's not what you think you should be

00:09:46.240 --> 00:09:47.910
doing at that moment. And the Lord

00:09:47.920 --> 00:09:50.310
showed me. He said, "It's not what you

00:09:50.320 --> 00:09:52.470
think you should be doing at the moment.

00:09:52.480 --> 00:09:54.790
It's following My voice, even if it

00:09:54.800 --> 00:09:57.269
doesn't make

00:09:57.269 --> 00:09:57.279
sense."And

00:09:57.279 --> 00:09:59.350
what we're going to come to

00:09:59.360 --> 00:10:02.070
in the days ahead,

00:10:02.080 --> 00:10:04.550
going into the fall, going into this

00:10:04.560 --> 00:10:07.269
new season, He said an acceleration

00:10:07.279 --> 00:10:10.310
of things is about to take place.

00:10:10.320 --> 00:10:12.150
You're about to see things change like

00:10:12.160 --> 00:10:15.110
you've never seen them change before. And

00:10:15.120 --> 00:10:17.190
if you want to flow with Me, you're

00:10:17.200 --> 00:10:19.110
going to have to obey Me when it doesn't

00:10:19.120 --> 00:10:21.110
make sense.

00:10:21.120 --> 00:10:22.550
And that's what He's been instructing me

00:10:22.560 --> 00:10:23.829
about.

00:10:23.839 --> 00:10:25.670
I was invited to do certain

00:10:25.680 --> 00:10:29.750
things, and it looked all beautiful,

00:10:29.760 --> 00:10:31.350
but the Lord said, "This is not peace.

00:10:31.360 --> 00:10:34.790
I'm not giving you a go on

